### Invoice Analyzer API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get API Documentation
GET {{baseUrl}}/docs

###

### Get OpenAPI Schema
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi.json

###

### Analyze Invoice - Test with sample image
POST {{baseUrl}}/analyze-invoice
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test_invoice.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test_invoice.png
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

